<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <!-- Hero Widget ******************* -->
  <div class="w-9/12 mx-auto">
    <Hero
      tagline="Contact Us"
      image={{
        src: '/area/reception.jpg',
        alt: 'Caos Image',
      }}
    >
      <Fragment slot="title"> About Pine Hill Resort </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="subtitle">
        <div class="text-justify text-gray-500">
          Located in a scenic hilly region, 4200+ feet above sea level, Pine Hill Resort ensures a tranquil atmosphere
          and gracious services with pleasant, peaceful and picturesque landscaping surrounded by pine trees and misty
          mountains accompanied by cooling fresh breezes. Situated near the center of Kalaw, most of the town, including
          the central market and the restaurants, is in walking distance. While at our resort, you can also give a tour
          to our famous garden crowned with rare and precious orchids. Our reception and lobby building is also known
          for being one of the oldest British Colonial houses in the country. If you are looking for a place to escape
          from your daily stress or the heat of lowlands, Pine Hill Resort is the right choice for you. This is where
          serenity becomes reality!
        </div>
      </Fragment>
    </Hero>

